                        knew how to keep myself on track. ALFA is easy to use and makes sticking to a workout plan a breeze. 
                        With ALFA, there's really no excuse to workout!"</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row userRow">
                        <div class="col-sm-3 imgCol">
                            <img src="~/Content/images/becca.jpg" /> - Becca B.
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-8 userText">"Before ALFA, I wrote out the exercises I wanted to complete for a workout by hand. If I 
