                        a workout with ease and all my workouts stay organized."</div>
                        <div class="col"></div>
                    </div>         
                    <div class="row userRow lastUser">
                        <div class="col-sm-3 imgCol">
                            <img src="~/Content/images/micah.jpeg" />- Micah K.
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-8 userText">"ALFA keeps all my workouts organized so that I can plan out the different workouts 
                        to complete on different days. This has really helped me maintain consistency in my workouts and makes it easy to 
