                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5">
                <div class="container customWktsBox">
                    <div class="row">
                        <h5 class="col infoHeader">1) Create Custom Workouts!</h5>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col infoText">
                            <ul>
                                <li>Name each workout to help keep your workout plan organized.</li>
                                <li>Select as many exercises as you want to add to a workout.</li>
                                <li>Change the order of exercises or delete them if you change your mind.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-1"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="container excBox">
                    <div class="row">
                        <h5 class="col infoHeader">2) Modify Sets/Goals</h5>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col infoText">
                            <ul>
                                <li>Add a goal for an exercise by setting the number of reps, amount of weight, duration, or mileage.</li>
                                <li>Met your goal?? ALFA makes it easy to edit goals as you progress.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-1"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="container setBox">
                    <div class="row">
                        <h5 class="col infoHeader">3) Enter Workout Mode!</h5>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col infoText">
                            <ul>
                                <li>Workout Mode allows you to view each exercise as you complete them.</li>
                                <li>After you complete an exercise, hit Next for the next exercise to appear.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-1"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
